Interface BuildInfo

All Known Implementing Classes:
CoreUtilsBuildInfo, MavenBuildInfo
public interface BuildInfo
This interface represents the build-information that is usually collected by build-tool into some dedicated text-resource, which are available in classpath at runtime.
